SEEED XIAO ESP32-C3 sketch for WSPR. 

Sketch will compile on Arduino IDE and VSC.

Hardware consits of SEEED XIAO ESP32-C3 and SI5351 syntisizer. Time syncronisation either via WiFi NTP server or manual by pressing knob on start of even minute.

Firmware has a webservice to config , calibrate and test the unit.
Unit has further a small amplifier with BS170 fet to raise the RF signal from 10 mW to 200 mW and additional LPF. 

Futher info will be disclosed when available

vy 73 de Johan, PA3ANG https://pa3ang.nl

more info in my weblog https://pa3ang.nl/esp32-c3-wspr/
